subject: Create SOFR collector with NY Fed primary and FRED fallback
description:
Create SOFRCollector extending BaseCollector[pd.DataFrame] with:
- Tier 1: NY Fed Markets API (https://markets.newyorkfed.org/api/rates/secured/sofr/last/{n}.json)
- Tier 2: FRED via OpenBB (SOFR series)
- Tier 3: Cached baseline (4.35%, Jan 2026)
Standard output columns: timestamp, series_id, source, value, unit
activeForm: Creating SOFR collector with multi-tier fallback
